  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Hemp Carbon Capture and Rural Development",
  "purpose": "To support domestic hemp in achieving the UK’s climate, energy and economic goals - with a particular focus on Sustainable Aviation Fuel, marine biofuels, sustainable construction, carbon credits, farming jobs and rural development. The Group will encourage investment in carbon capture, break down regulatory barriers and support a thriving domestic hemp sector.",
